			<h2>About</h2>

			<img src="img/about-logo.jpg" alt="" align="right" style="padding-left: 20px; padding-bottom: 20px;" />

			<p>My name is Peter Perry and I have been running this small family business
			since 1990. Providing a personal and professional service to our customers.</p>

			<p>We at PnP like to concentrate on customer recommendations. 95% of our business
			is based on these recommendations. Apart from <a href="http://www.yell.com" target="_blank" title="Yell.com">
			yell.com</a> we have never found the need to advertise,	our satisfied customers do that
			job for us!</p>

			<p><strong><em>We strive to achieve Quality as well as Quantity!</em></strong></p>

			<p>PnP can provide you with the following services:</p>

			<ul>
				<li>Internal re-decorating</li>
				<li>External re-decorating</li>
				<li>Wallpapering</li>
				<li>Coving &amp; Plastering Service</li>
				<li>Residential &amp; Commerical Work</li>
				<li>Floor Sanding &amp; Restoration</li>
				<li>Prompt Clean &amp; Tidy Service</li>
				<li>All Our Operatives Wear PnP Logo'd Uniforms</li>
			</ul>

			<p>Over the years we have mainly carried out residential projects on private
			customers property's also working for various estate agents and on landlord's
			portfolios.</p>

			<p>Our main customer base is the NW area of London and the home counties from
			Knebworth down to the west end, to Feltham in the west and across to Romford in
			the east. We have also worked in other parts of the country for our landlords
			who have properties in various areas including Bath, Bristol, Rugby and Kent.</p>

			<p>We can provide an out of hours service if required for shops, offices etc.
			Also we can provide labour to work weekends if required.</p>

			<p>We have also carried out works on schools, public houses and hotels.</p>

			<p>PnP can carry out a complete refurbishment, to the re-decoration of a small
			bedroom or a downstairs cloakroom in our eyes they are all as important as they
			all lead to recommendations to neighbours, friends &amp; family.</p>

			<p>Recommend us to a friend that I will guarantee.</p>
